started to dawn on me

00:07:05.035 --> 00:07:07.029
is that once I had,
maybe 100 or 200 videos

00:07:07.029 --> 00:07:09.221
for my cousins, is you
know, that's a pretty good

00:07:09.221 --> 00:07:11.350
scaffold of algebra and I said,

00:07:11.350 --> 00:07:12.665
"Oh! I wonder if I can do trigonometry?"

00:07:12.665 --> 00:07:14.413
So, another 100 videos later I was like,

00:07:14.413 --> 00:07:15.606
"Hey, that's a pretty good scaffold.

00:07:15.606 --> 00:07:17.074
You can always do more,
but that kind of gets

00:07:17.074 --> 00:07:18.654
the job done for a lot of people."

00:07:18.654 --> 00:07:20.071
I said, "Let me try to do calculus.

00:07:20.071 --> 00:07:21.922
Let me try to do physics.
Let me try to do chemistry.

00:07:21.922 --> 00:07:23.468
Let me try to do organic
chemistry." (laughing)

