provide the experience

00:42:04.450 --> 00:42:06.851
of a real course online
where homework's due

00:42:06.851 --> 00:42:09.568
every week, so the students
will quickly find out

00:42:09.568 --> 00:42:12.897
can they do the homework or not and

00:42:12.897 --> 00:42:14.187
we'll expect them to keep up.

00:42:14.356 --> 00:42:15.882
Tom: So, that raises
a couple of questions,

00:42:15.882 --> 00:42:17.679
but the first one is, just this 58,000

