and maybe it's more than
that by now, but this ...

00:42:19.741 --> 00:42:22.129
Peter: Yeah, but we're
just about at 85,000 now.

00:42:22.129 --> 00:42:25.951
Tom: 85,000? Did you have any expectation

00:42:25.951 --> 00:42:28.782
when you stepped up to offer this course,

00:42:28.782 --> 00:42:30.251
Peter Norvig, that you would attract

00:42:30.251 --> 00:42:31.465
that kind of audience?

